                    <value>&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hello {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Directions for CJC-1295/Ipamorelin are as followed:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Step 1: Flip off colored plastic cap/tear off center seal from the CJC-1295/Ipamorelin vial and wipe the top with alcohol swab.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 2: Remove cap from the provided water and wipe the top with alcohol swab.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 3: Using the mixing syringe, turn the bottle of water upside down and insert the needle and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;draw 5ml of water.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 4: Remove the syringe from vial with Bacteriostatic Water and inject slowly into the CJC/Ipamorelin powder.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 5: Swirl the vial around until solution is clear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 6: Discard any Bacteriostatic Water left from the original Bacteriostatic Water vial and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;refrigerate CJC-1295/Ipamorelin after reconstitution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;**Please note that each time prior to inserting the syringe into the CJC-1295/Ipamorelin vial you should always wipe the top of the vial first**&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
{{{Sender.FirstName}}}&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X &lt;/span&gt;Health&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Main: 305.682.1818&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;</value>
